ddGroup.title: How can I become part of the community?
content: Join our discord and get OG and Hyperlist roles.

ddGroup.title: What is Hyperlty?
content: Hyperlty is a pool for holders. The money from the Hyperlty will be used to buy Blue Chip NFT, which holders will be able to receive in exchange for $Hypers on the raffle platform.

ddGroup.title: Where will Hyperlty's liquidity come from?
content: We will monetize our main platforms: launchpad, staking, raffles. Projects that will be hosted on these platforms will pay a commission. Also, all royalties from secondary NFT sales will go to Hyperlty.

ddGroup.title: When mint and NFT price?
content: All the details are in our discord. We will be glad to see you there!
